    <title>Django学习笔记</title>
    <url>/2020/02/17/Django%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>环境<ul>
<li>Python3.6</li>
<li>django1.8</li>
</ul>
